### 用户积分系统 API 测试文件
### 项目：jike-web-api
### 接口版本：v1
### 说明：测试 VIP 积分增减接口

### ====================================
### 配置信息
### ====================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:9001
@contentType = application/json

### 用户认证信息
### 获取方式：完成登录后，从响应中复制 token
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJpb3QtYXBwLXNlcnZlciIsInN1YiI6IjIwNDExNDAwMjE5MzQxMzczNDQiLCJhdWQiOlsiaW90LWFwcCJdLCJleHAiOjE3ODEyNjI3NDEsImlhdCI6MTc3NjA3ODc0MSwianRpIjoiMTI4Y2Q4YjAtMzBkMS00OWQyLTgzNTktYTBkZjBmN2VmN2FiIiwiZGV2aWNlSWQiOiIifQ.bPD1xrpdnAeukK5-gFDD8jqZKDfPd7sqr54ad39JvwU
@userId = 2041140021934137344

### 测试用例的用户 ID（可根据实际情况修改）
@testUserId = 2041140021934137344
@addVipScore = 100
@subtractVipScore = 50
@excessiveSubtractScore = 999999

### ====================================
### 1. 积分查询接口
### ====================================

### 1.1 查询用户积分余额（用于验证当前状态）
GET {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/balance-info
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### ====================================
### 2. VIP 积分增加测试
### ====================================

### 2.1 增加 100 VIP 积分 - 正常场景
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": {{addVipScore}}
}

###

### 2.2 增加 500 VIP 积分
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": 500
}

###

### ====================================
### 3. VIP 积分减少测试
### ====================================

### 3.1 减少 50 VIP 积分 - 正常场景
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": {{subtractVipScore}}
}

###

### 3.2 减少 200 VIP 积分
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": -200
}

###

### ====================================
### 4. 错误场景测试
### ====================================

### 4.1 余额不足 - 尝试减少超大数值
### 预期：返回错误信息 "VIP 积分余额不足"
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": -{{excessiveSubtractScore}}
}

###

### 4.2 VIP 积分变化量为 0 - 参数验证失败
### 预期：返回参数错误信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": 0
}

###

### 4.3 缺少 userId 参数 - 参数验证失败
### 预期：返回参数错误信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "vipScoreDelta": 100
}

###

### 4.4 userId 为负数 - 参数验证失败
### 预期：返回参数错误信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: {{token}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": -1,
  "vipScoreDelta": 100
}

###

### 4.5 缺少 token - 认证失败
### 预期：返回认证失败信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": 100
}

###

### 4.6 token 无效 - 认证失败
### 预期：返回认证失败信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/userscore/v1/update-vip-score
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
x-token: invalid_token
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": {{testUserId}},
  "vipScoreDelta": 100
}

###

